01:30.671 --> 01:31.632
Were they... There's a Dixie Chicken and some more 
stuff in there that didn't exist. All right, Lupo

01:38.829 --> 01:42.072
wasn't there yet, was he?

01:45.396 --> 01:46.977
Yeah, Lou came in. He was more or less on the west 
side of the street. On that corner? Yeah, he came in

