top of the academic building, and it would be, 
they'd let them go, they'd let them go around, and

29:29.324 --> 29:53.530
they'd let it fall out, and outside

29:29.324 --> 29:53.530
they'd go on, and be there for the ceremony. There 
was no, there was no enunciation, since

29:58.535 --> 30:26.365
you your final semester or so you were not in the 
core you didn't go through a final review as a

29:58.535 --> 30:26.365
senior did you oh did you describe it where was it 
held but

