What

30:27.256 --> 30:50.799
about Aggie Muster in those days? Very informal. 
Held where? To tell you the truth, I don't remember

30:56.180 --> 31:00.466
one on the campus. The first muster I became 
acquainted with was when I was working

31:00.486 --> 31:17.650
in Houston about 1950. And it was basically a beer 
busted swimming club. So that's gotten much more

31:20.875 --> 31:22.697
serious. Oh, yeah. It's gotten far more serious. 
